{"tid":2426171,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"估計名潮食館爆疫源頭為該食肆一名清潔員工，涉及一名72歲男子，居於秀茂坪邨秀康樓","createTime":"2021-02-28T01:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T01:17:41.000Z","uid":237459,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f60f5081ac4775294511dc7ff18169b7e7c97f8","tid":2426171,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:05:56.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心早前曾表示，估計名潮食館爆疫源頭為該食肆一名清潔員工，涉及一名72歲男子，居於秀茂坪邨秀康樓，他於本月14日曾做病毒檢測，當時結果沒有確診，其後於18日出現咳嗽病徵，翌日仍有上班至下午4時。"},{"pid":"6148f977fb20e2371f76d009a1fdb679b5d7b55d","tid":2426171,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">曾做病毒檢測</span></blockquote>明明深喉完，點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話做完檢測就有抗體<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d9a22d843c71616fc19460f47826c1f90acd2b","tid":2426171,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:15:28.000Z","msg":"廢老廢邨"},{"pid":"9a3d5f6a05e044caaacaaa42b050172491d46233","tid":2426171,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47d9a22d843c71616fc19460f47826c1f90acd2b","tid":2426171,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:15:28.000Z","msg":"廢老廢邨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}